{"tid":2407234,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"$6000蚊點買RTX 3060 laptop","createTime":"2021-02-14T00:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T02:49:13.000Z","uid":127905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d445af09ee7beee03b59785af6eeaef015e5dfa6","tid":2407234,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T00:49:33.000Z","msg":"北京一名為「魚池青青」的網紅，近日在影片平台嗶哩嗶哩（Bilibili，B站）上傳教學影片，向網民示範自己如何使用搭載NVIDIA RTX 3060顯示卡的電競手提電腦便能成功在星巴克內「挖礦」，即賺取加密貨幣，如比特幣（Bitcoin）、以太幣（Ether）等。她指自己在店內呆坐4小時，當天即獲得了4.5元（人民幣．下同）收入。<br />\n...<br />\n她以該電競手提電腦的效能及以太幣當天的價值推算，如果用這種方式挖礦，每日可賺約23元人民幣，<span class=\"red\"><strong>約260天就能賺6000元的電腦成本價</strong></span>，倘進行超頻後，回本期甚至可以更短。最終，其在星巴克逗留4個小時後，獲4.5元收益，由於星巴克三里屯店非24小時營業，她還建議網民晚上可以到麥當勞繼續挖礦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/587269/starbucks%E5%91%86%E5%9D%904%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E8%B3%BA4-5%E5%85%83-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%95%99%E9%9B%B6%E9%9B%BB%E8%B2%BB-%E6%8C%96%E7%A4%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F587269%2Fstarbucks%25E5%2591%2586%25E5%259D%25904%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25B3%25BA4-5%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2595%2599%25E9%259B%25B6%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E6%258C%2596%25E7%25A4%25A6&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=96fb4bf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/587269/starbucks%E5%91%86%E5%9D%904%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E8%B3%BA4-5%E5%85%83-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%95%99%E9%9B%B6%E9%9B%BB%E8%B2%BB-%E6%8C%96%E7%A4%A6</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇大佬知邊度有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces